{"id": "1189698573923790848", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "我还是要安利我都这篇文章，里面讲述了神王图鲁的开大收益公式。", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:37:23.554000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189698995744948265", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "装备方面，考虑性价比和生存的问题。有些装备，像海之梦，其实带了没有任何效果。除非赌起手海之梦，中局根本不能左右局势的变化", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:39:04.124000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189699411656327269", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "反击鱼鳍同理。这些装备虽然有数值，但是不能对局时产生根本性的改变。你带了还不如不带，浪费算力", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:40:43.285000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189699754293219489", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "希翼虽小，1费3层阻挡，足以顶30层伤害。急时能救命，不急也白赚，亏了都不亏。", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:42:04.976000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189700924764061838", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "嗯，認真看了，之後也認真實戰了，盡量讓每個開大的回合都能開出2-3次大", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:46:44.038000+00:00", "type": 19, "reply_to": "1189698573923790848"}
{"id": "1189701111431577641", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "2-3次大击杀对方两个人左右是常见的。其余的就是临场操作决定的了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:47:28.543000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701256038600795", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "不過希冀很容易被對面朵兒連加固帶盾一起驅掉……因為只有一個坦", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:48:03.020000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701366449438772", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "驱散2费，交了是好事", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:48:29.344000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701403132841984", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "我不知道為什麼總是只能打掉一個，最多讓第二個殘血", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:48:38.090000+00:00", "type": 19, "reply_to": "1189701111431577641"}
{"id": "1189701460334739581", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "你希翼不会给骑士用的吧。", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:48:51.728000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701527493951568", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "过度防守结果被驱散浪费了。", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:49:07.740000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701606439125062", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "希冀是取當前血量最低的", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:49:26.562000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701623031803974", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "因为有阻挡先结算阻挡，护盾会过期。护盾套阻挡是无用防守", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:49:30.518000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701690694312006", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "我一般希翼给朵儿。", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:49:46.650000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701790329999430", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "当然，我舍弃复活甲了。因为我觉得朵儿先不先死都一样", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:50:10.405000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189701919325822996", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "朵儿先死和后死之间的收益差距小于复活甲的费用，4费", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:50:41.160000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702193327132822", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "希翼还有一个用法，就是神王没来，但是你图鲁第一回合就能开大。你直接给朵儿套3层阻挡", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:51:46.487000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702285664731197", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "图鲁先用希翼开大，然后神王再替掉", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:52:08.502000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702381496184963", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "！學到了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:52:31.350000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702471241699459", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "那鑰令那張卡推薦帶嗎？", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:52:52.747000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702570764144670", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "聚首一般，因为不稳定，不知道来哪张", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:53:16.475000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702622127603742", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "愿意赌就可以带，不愿意赌就拉倒了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:53:28.721000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702760782909492", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "好的，筆記筆記，第四人是諾締拉還是奧吉爾好一些呢？", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:54:01.779000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189702938373923007", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "奥吉尔。奥吉尔更灵活，输出更多，进攻性更强", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:54:44.120000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703151234854933", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "講究一個速攻？那2費易傷可以單丟嗎？", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:55:34.870000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703244767830056", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "不可以。易伤追求和图鲁开大同步", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:55:57.170000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703260714569830", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "我通常是3、2費一套點名，但是經常湊不到牌奧就沒了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:00.972000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703265445761064", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "也不要轻易丢给残血", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:02.100000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703366465572904", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "比如前排残，后排肉，你先开大收掉残血，再给后排一个易伤，再开大", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:26.185000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703388762488946", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "啊，是配合圖開大單丟，但不丟點名", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:31.501000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703421637431376", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "点名如果没有击杀就没有意义了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:39.339000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703479107796992", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "点名如果不能快速达成击杀，就要用雪花换掉", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:56:53.041000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703559776845884", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "能斩杀就可以丢这个5费comb", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:57:12.274000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703643855855776", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "鑰令帶雪花？", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:57:32.320000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703688147705980", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "雪花换牌会加速下一轮牌库刷新，这样你在残局更容易快人一步", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:57:42.880000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🆗", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1189703718157950996", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "带", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:57:50.035000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703773778612295", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "要替狂氣還是算力呢？", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:58:03.296000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703823942504448", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "神王的上手速度决定了卡组的启动速度，如果神王不来，卡组不成立", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:58:15.256000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189703925855698954", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "算力，这样防止没有费用上神王，卡一手牌的尴尬情况", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:58:39.554000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704039890440203", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "鼠鼠的智慧是真的很有智慧", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:06.742000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704065295331488", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "那開場發牌有算力有神王就直接上嗎？還是有其他的講究", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:12.799000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704068562698281", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "基本鼠鼠跟神王绑在一起了", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:13.578000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704114733580390", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "content": "神王自然是越早越好", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:24.586000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704162238275787", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "好的，學到很多，謝謝佬", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:35.912000+00:00"}
{"id": "1189704183620849676", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "content": "https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/942776001321115730/1035245796351819796/61587f803fb8da40b608e652qedg6psj02_2021_12_07_16_53_19.gif", "timestamp": "2023-12-27T22:59:41.010000+00:00", "embeds": [{"type": "image", "title": "", "url": "https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/942776001321115730/1035245796351819796/61587f803fb8da40b608e652qedg6psj02_2021_12_07_16_53_19.gif", "description": ""}]}
